From 77b4ea32d1094b54cb191ef7e7cf9c836775f854 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Yingjie Shang <dev@yingjie.dev>
Date: Tue, 16 Jun 2026 20:36:08 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/5] fix(random): seed Rand::new() from platform entropy

- Add @env.rand(n) -> Bytes? for native, JS, and WASM/WASM-GC
- Native uses getrandom(2); JS uses crypto.getRandomValues
- WASM/WASM-GC returns None until raw pointer FFI is available
- Update Rand::new() to prefer OS entropy and fall back to time+counter
- Make deterministic tests use explicit Rand::chacha8(seed=)
- Add regression test that two Rand::new() instances differ
